[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m **SSTI Tested:**                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m Tested Server-Side Template Injection on `/name/set` with `{{7*7}}` payload. [2;36m│[0m
